e. This means you can't hear, see, or touch anything. Imagine yourself trap=
ped in a soundproof chamber.</p>
<p class=3D"qtext_para" style=3D"margin:1em 0; display:inline-block; margin=
-bottom:1em">Microsoft has this =E2=80=94 they are testing equipment there.=
 The noise level inside is a record-20.35 decibels. To make the camera even=
