uting into the pillow. Microsoft uses the audio lab to improve its own prod=
ucts. For example, it can enhance the "hearing" of the voice assistant when=
 the user accesses a Windows device from the other end of the room, and tab=
lets and laptops-to learn to perceive subtle signals.</p>
